7 Nov 2016The Economic Sectors, Employment and Infrastructure Development Cluster led by Minister of Rural Development and Land Reform, Gugile Nkwinti will on Monday 07 November 2016 visit the site of the Agri-hub in Moretele in the Northwest Province and conduct a community Imbizo with residents. Members of the media are invited to cover the event as follows: Date: 07 November 2016 Time: 10h00 Venue: Moretele Municipality ( Makapanstad village) The event forms part of the fifth Imbizo Focus Week programme which takes place between 7 and 11 November 2016, under the theme "Together we move South Africa forward: Our future make it work." Media RSVPs and Enquiries should be directed to: Tshepo Diale on 071 850 1751 Enquiries: Linda Page Contact: 083 460 4482 Issued by Government Communications and Information Systems (GCIS)